Arch Rogue — Third-Party Notices and AI Provenance
==================================================

This file is the canonical third-party attribution list for the Arch Rogue
Android APK distribution. It reflects the pinned python-for-android distribution
and the codec/font/image components enabled by its SDL2 bootstrap. A copy is
bundled inside the APK as `assets/licenses/NOTICE.txt` and surfaced from the
in-app About → Open Source Licenses screen.

The Arch Rogue project code itself is licensed under the Apache License 2.0
(see `LICENSE` / `assets/licenses/LICENSE.txt`). pygame-ce is LGPL-2.1-or-later;
the full LGPL text is bundled as `assets/licenses/LGPL-2.1.txt` and displayed
in-app. Other components retain the licenses listed below.

