Build-tool attribution (NOT bundled in the APK)
------------------------------------------------

buildozer and python-for-android are (L)GPL build tools. They compile the APK on
the host but their source is never packaged into the shipped APK. The validator
rejects any APK whose `assets/private.tar` contains `buildozer/` or
`pythonforandroid/` source, so an accidental bundling of build-tool source
cannot ship.

